name: Fabrication API
description: Nodes for working with the Revit Fabrication API
contents: AttachToStructure - Attach Fabrication hanger rod ends to nearest structural member., Fabrication Part Dimensions - Retrieve an array of FabricationPart dimensions., FabricationPart.IsSameAs - Groups FabricationParts into sublists of identical parts, as determined by optional ignoreFields., SetDimensionValue - Set dimension values for FabricationParts.
